{"tid":2450263,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"吳鎮宇2021新片濁水漂流 好似冇咩人知","createTime":"2021-03-17T09:17:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-20T05:18:11.000Z","uid":23707,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"02a4a65480cbe3a5475ec7cf538ea0f246c17208","tid":2450263,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T09:17:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HNmH6Fu3Up8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DHNmH6Fu3Up8&d=V7AID%2B4Ek1BfB0hSL70CTy%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=d9f5e5a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HNmH6Fu3Up8</a><br />\n<br />\n《濁水漂流》（英文：Drifting）是2021年香港真人真事改編劇情片，由李駿碩編導，吳鎮宇、謝君豪、李麗珍、蔡思韵、朱栢康、寶珮如和柯煒林主演[1]。講述一班於深水埗天橋底下聚居的露宿者被社會邊緣化，他們因為城市再發展而長期遭到掃蕩清場的故事[2]。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢年啲港產片搞咩咁高汁<br />\n套套都好似入場睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請支持港產片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e58816f48e9b603f5c01a0c7e5a5a0e159dcde6","tid":2450263,"uid":3326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T09:55:05.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"8aeb2b5af4931f4a115c1de29b61d949ebdb93dc","tid":2450263,"uid":30084,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T09:57:05.000Z","msg":"就算拍呢種片 <br />\n金像獎 一樣冇佢份 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小圈子正仆街"},{"pid":"d6ec1b17da1bf17677c5ef944cd218ab8812a42c","tid":2450263,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T12:05:39.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ce8f74c318b3ad8f0d774447d1d4c5f8e1e94786","tid":2450263,"uid":10454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T14:30:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1/601424/%E5%B0%8B%E7%A7%A6%E8%A8%98-%E5%85%AC%E4%BB%94t%E6%81%A4%E6%B7%98%E5%AF%B6%E6%9C%89%E5%94%AE-%E9%87%91%E5%83%8F%E7%8D%8E%E7%BE%8E%E6%8C%87%